<p><b>Adam Ries</b> (1492 – March 30, 1559) was a <a href="/wiki/Germans" title="Germans">German</a> <a href="/wiki/Mathematician" title="Mathematician">mathematician</a>. He is <a href="#Name">also known</a> by the name <b>Adam Riese</b>.<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<p></p>
<div id="toc" class="toc">
<div id="toctitle">
